  <data key="d2">2</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PERSONAL PROPERTY TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FINANCIAL_CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A type of tax levied on personal possessions, such as a car.</data>
  <data key="d2">2</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CAR TAX&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FINANCIAL_CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A specific example of personal property tax.</data>
  <data key="d2">2</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ESTATE PLANNING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FINANCIAL_CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The process of preparing for the transfer of a person's assets and wealth after their death, often involving wills and trusts.</data>
  <data key="d2">1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;WILL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FINANCIAL_PRODUCT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A legal document specifying how a person's property will be distributed after their death.</data>
  <data key="d2">2</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TRUST&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FINANCIAL_PRODUCT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A legal document that holds the property transferred to it and can be given to a trusted loved one before death.</data>
  <data key="d2">2</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FAMILY CONFLICTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"RISK"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Potential disagreements or disputes among family members that can arise after a person's death, which can be mitigated by estate planning documents.</data>
  <data key="d2">1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LEGAL TIME&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"RISK"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The duration of legal proceedings, which can be reduced by having proper estate planning documents in place.</data>
  <data key="d2">1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FINANCIAL COSTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"RISK"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Expenses incurred during legal processes or estate administration, which can be minimized through proper estate planning.</data>
  <data key="d2">1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LOSING A LOVED ONE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A stressful life event that prompts the need for organized financial and medical documents to minimize family conflicts, legal time, and financial costs.</data>
  <data key="d2">1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FINANCIAL PLANNERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Professionals who can assist in the creation of wills and trusts.</data>
  <data key="d2">2</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LEGAL AID OFFICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"An office providing legal assistance, including help with creating wills or trusts.</data>
  <data key="d2">2</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LIVING WILL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FINANCIAL_PRODUCT"</data>
